{"id":611304,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/05/巴丢草-我要说话-我要画画-我回来了/","date":"2019-05-28T10:27:14Z","modified":"2019-05-28T10:27:14Z","title":"巴丢草 | 我要说话 我要画画 我回来了","content":"<p>@badiucao：草泥马审查！我要说话，我要画画，我回来了！我的纪录片#ChinasArtfulDissident 将在 #六四30周年 @ABCTV 首播，期待大家。Screw the censorship! I am back with my documentary #ChinasArtfulDissident. Let&#8217;s make noise! #badiucao  Airs Tuesday 4 June on @ABCTV</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">草泥马审查！<br />我要说话，我要画画，我回来了！<br />我的纪录片#ChinasArtfulDissident 将在 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B30%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#六四30周年</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ABCTV?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ABCTV</a> 首播，期待大家。<br />Screw the censorship! I am back with my documentary<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ChinasArtfulDissident?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ChinasArtfulDissident</a>. Let&#39;s make noise! <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/badiucao?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#badiucao</a></p>\n<p>Airs Tuesday 4 June on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ABCTV?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ABCTV</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/H3JUEJGrpX\">pic.twitter.com/H3JUEJGrpX</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 巴丢草  Badiucao (@badiucao) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/badiucao/status/1133175381647810560?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 28, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">🎬<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/HongKong?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#HongKong</a> premiere of ‘<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/China?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#China</a>’s Artful Dissident’ – a film about political cartoonist Badiucao.</p>\n<p>🎫Limited tickets: <a href=\"https://t.co/ACjPFYXIMM\">https://t.co/ACjPFYXIMM</a> </p>\n<p>Monday, June 10, 8pm at Hive Spring. HK$80. Includes Q&amp;A with artist <a href=\"https://twitter.com/badiucao?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@Badiucao</a>, director <a href=\"https://twitter.com/dannyb_m?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@dannyb_m</a> &amp; the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/HKJA_Official?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@HKJA_Official</a>&#39;s Shirley Yam. <a href=\"https://t.co/LPHKQIxOGo\">pic.twitter.com/LPHKQIxOGo</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Hong Kong Free Press (@HongKongFP) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/HongKongFP/status/1133293528082108416?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 28, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">Here is the poster for <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ChinasArtfulDissident?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ChinasArtfulDissident</a>. <br />100% <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/badiucao?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#badiucao</a> style! </p>\n<p>自己的电影，当然要自己设计海报，拿去拿去：）</p>\n<p>The film airs Tuesday 4 June on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ABCTV?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ABCTV</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/4v3OXSj7oe\">pic.twitter.com/4v3OXSj7oe</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 巴丢草  Badiucao (@badiucao) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/badiucao/status/1133295880855908353?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 28, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Badiucao, “China’s Artful Dissident” <a href=\"https://t.co/H1TuTD2a53\">https://t.co/H1TuTD2a53</a> New film by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/dannyb_m?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@dannyb_m</a> on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/badiucao?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@badiucao</a> to premiere June 4th on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/abcnews?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@abcnews</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; China Di